    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的游戏机制</h2>玩家可以自由操控重力来探索关卡。在改变重力的同时，玩家也会改变对应的颜色。<br>相同颜色的角色只能站在对应的平台上。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=584 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的玩法</h2>游戏共有六个章节，超过八十个关卡。<br>每个章节都有不同的机制和玩法。<br>在每个章节中，玩家都将体验不一样的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遇见过去的自己</h2>如果能见到儿时的自己，你会对她说什么呢？在错乱的时空中，长大后的主角遇到了过去的自己。两个人必须齐心协力才能逃离这个时空。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无障碍设置</h2>盲人玩家也可以游玩《红与黑》！！！<br>通过游戏的无障碍设置，盲人玩家也可以享受解谜和动作游戏的乐趣。<br>此模式需要开启NVDA或调用NVDA接口进行体验。",
